{"tid":1674162,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"對川普低頭   南韓放棄WTO發展中國家定位","createTime":"2019-10-25T05:00:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T11:52:36.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c69c6e6a22f6df2237c47509a8fa4d27851d8879","tid":1674162,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:00:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2019/10/25/phpa7pjF9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F10%2F25%2Fphpa7pjF9.jpg&h=b20bf12b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南韓放棄WTO發展中國家地位。圖左為美國總統川普，右為南韓總統文在寅。（資料照，美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普指控一些全球最富有的國家，濫用WTO開發中國家地位，南韓則是被川普點名的國家之一。針對此事，南韓貿易官員本週已與美方官員展開討論，最新消息指出，南韓已經決定放棄WTO開發中國家地位。<br />\n<br />\n《韓聯社》報導，南韓政府25日召開對外經濟部門長官會議，決定放棄WTO開發中國家地位，在WTO新談判達成協議前，南韓可繼續享受WTO向開發中國家提供的優惠，由於談判耗時較長，政府盡可能對稻米等農業領域加以保護。<br />\n<br />\n南韓是在1995年以開發中國家地位加入WTO，若南韓不是開發中國家地位，南韓當局將無法藉高關稅保護市場，農產品價格也無法透過補貼維持競爭力，讓該國農業直接遭受衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n川普今年7月在備忘錄提到，近3分之2的WTO成員利用宣稱自己是「開發中國家」，以獲取特殊待遇；世界10大最富裕經濟體中，就有7個宣稱是「開發中」地位，即汶萊、香港、科威特、澳門、卡達、新加坡、阿拉伯聯合大公國；中國、墨西哥、南韓和土耳其都已是G20成員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2956987\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2956987&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTRR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=3af1ebc2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2956987&h=5c59a2e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2956987</a>"},{"pid":"6ab37645b8697179cd3e9083da9505956506f25a","tid":1674162,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:00:38.000Z","msg":"西朝鮮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e257c5b14184006a5725495645fe8d06b35a4374","tid":1674162,"uid":41545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:04:17.000Z","msg":"中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad0160f41a7a052104f6b69ba649f577fa64075b","tid":1674162,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:04:54.000Z","msg":"香港有宣稱 係開發中咩？"},{"pid":"fe92913cea94728dbff4b0d8ba4f6118623a6c64","tid":1674162,"uid":87305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:06:05.000Z","msg":"韓國比中國強大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee78f40827ded414bde4d7c6bb8143c5b7fb70b","tid":1674162,"uid":26333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:06:29.000Z","msg":"點㸃名就自己放棄發展中國家地位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab106deb257c215b76312c3f4962cc6c9a59e250","tid":1674162,"uid":169801,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c69c6e6a22f6df2237c47509a8fa4d27851d8879","tid":1674162,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:00:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2019/10/25/phpa7pjF9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F10%2F25%2Fphpa7pjF9.jpg&h=b20bf12b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南韓放棄WTO發展中國家地位。圖左為美國總統川普，右為南韓總統文在寅。（資料照，美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普指控一些全球最富有的國家，濫用WTO開發中國家地位，南韓則是被川普點名的國家之一。針對此事，南韓貿易官員本週已與美方官員展開討論，最新消息指出，南韓已經決定放棄WTO開發中國家地位。<br />\n<br />\n《韓聯社》報導，南韓政府25日召開對外經濟部門長官會議，決定放棄WTO開發中國家地位，在WTO新談判達成協議前，南韓可繼續享受WTO向開發中國家提供的優惠，由於談判耗時較長，政府盡可能對稻米等農業領域加以保護。<br />\n<br />\n南韓是在1995年以開發中國家地位加入WTO，若南韓不是開發中國家地位，南韓當局將無法藉高關稅保護市場，農產品價格也無法透過補貼維持競爭力，讓該國農業直接遭受衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n川普今年7月在備忘錄提到，近3分之2的WTO成員利用宣稱自己是「開發中國家」，以獲取特殊待遇；世界10大最富裕經濟體中，就有7個宣稱是「開發中」地位，即汶萊、香港、科威特、澳門、卡達、新加坡、阿拉伯聯合大公國；中國、墨西哥、南韓和土耳其都已是G20成員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2956987\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2956987&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTRR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=3af1ebc2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2956987&h=5c59a2e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2956987</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:09:03.000Z","msg":"我依家先知南韓竟然都係發展中國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我一直以為得中國咁狗，好彩無藍絲識野，用呢個論點駁我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ddaaa14b977c824611cda190c3cda1477d3e530","tid":1674162,"uid":55973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:10:18.000Z","msg":"記得以前讀書個陣唔係話香港係已發展地區啦咩"},{"pid":"be354c1ebc7b6692e04eae04ee6bf0e7e72667cf","tid":1674162,"uid":34457,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:11:35.000Z","msg":"香港=民主開發中國家"},{"pid":"11b98cdec4b9e1dabf71c5d7a48fd7eb98852c12","tid":1674162,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad0160f41a7a052104f6b69ba649f577fa64075b","tid":1674162,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:04:54.000Z","msg":"香港有宣稱 係開發中咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:11:55.000Z","msg":"被開發"},{"pid":"ca061dead56c15f6577638c28149b945c9f7ef65","tid":1674162,"uid":76776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:12:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3afe416f8e110bcac2f747404818f2dba9f89a87","tid":1674162,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ee78f40827ded414bde4d7c6bb8143c5b7fb70b","tid":1674162,"uid":26333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:06:29.000Z","msg":"點㸃名就自己放棄發展中國家地位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" clas