n無恥真係無敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c1201b0c602cffc0564c5fdb36a90bc8f6801aa","tid":1674162,"uid":117332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:52:36.000Z","msg":"wto係無deveoping countries既working definition，佢操作上只依靠加入國自己宣稱。不過機制上可以由其他成員challenge 佢既發展中資格。<br />\n<br />\n所以無得借呢樣罵中國/韓國，因為wto本來就唔係個種發展/已發展既區分體系。韓國係佢依制度宣稱，美國都係依制度咁質疑啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能韓國都知點都講唔通，有人質疑咪放棄囉。"}]}